Jardine Lloyd Thompson Buys Stake in Chile Insurance Broker

-- B y   K e v i n   C r o w l e y
-- 
2011-06-28T08:11:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-28/jardine-lloyd-thompson-buys-stake-in-chile-insurance-broker-1-.html
Jardine Lloyd Thompson Group Plc (JLT) ,
the U.K.’s biggest publicly traded insurance broker, agreed to
buy a stake in Alta SA to expand in  Chile .  The company agreed to purchase an initial 50.1 percent
stake in Chile’s fourth-largest insurance broker and an option
to acquire a further 25 percent stake in 2020, London-based JLT
said in a statement today. Alta had net revenue of $8.1 million
in 2010.  JLT climbed 1.5 percent to 652 pence as of 9:10 a.m. in
London trading for a market value of 1.4 billion pounds ($2.2
billion).  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kevin Crowley in London at 
